What you need to know:

Southgate has overseen an impressive youth revolution since taking charge of England in 2016 and the delayed European Championship could be the perfect time for his labours to bear fruitSouthgate believes England have a golden opportunity to win a senior international prize for the first time since the 1966 World CupSouthgate's current crop will be helped by a tournament schedule that could see England play all but one of their games at Wembley if they reach the final